  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK390">
<l>koṭaiyaḷi ceṅkōl kuṭiyōmpa ṉāṉku</l>
<l>muṭaiyāṉām vēntark koḷi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is the light of kings who has there four things, beneficence, benevolence, rectitude, and care for his people.</l>
